docs/specs/rhei-transitions.spec.md:318:Transitions can be produced by seven distinct mechanisms. The `triggeredBy` field has four values (`user`, `callback`, `system`, `engine`) that classify these mechanisms — the three system-driven mechanisms (program exit-code, agent timeout, tooling-unavailable) all report `triggeredBy: 'system'`:
docs/specs/rhei-transitions.spec.md:320:### 1. User Trigger (`triggeredBy: 'user'`)
